{"type":"message","id":"c7ed585a","parentId":"2cd00e4e","timestamp":"2026-03-22T02:48:10.929Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"页面还是停留在专题首页，点击导航并没有跳转到文档详情页。这是因为这个页面使用的是Vue或React框架的单页应用，点击导航时是在右侧内容区域动态加载内容，而不是跳转新页面。\n\n让我尝试另一种方法：直接通过JavaScript查找右侧内容区域的容器，然后提取内容。或者我可以尝试通过URL直接访问每个文档的详情页。\n\n让我先尝试获取当前页面的完整HTML结构，看看文档链接的实际URL。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1c78f666f30440548f9b2ecc","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"\n() => {\n  // 查找所有包含\"文本字段\"的链接元素\n  const links = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('a, div[cursor=pointer], [role=button]')).filter(el => \n    el.textContent.trim() === '文本字段'\n  );\n  \n  // 获取这些元素的详细信息\n  return links.map(el => ({\n    tag: el.tagName,\n    text: el.textContent.trim(),\n    href: el.href || el.getAttribute('href') || 'no-href',\n    onclick: el.onclick ? 'has-onclick' : 'no-onclick',\n    classList: Array.from(el.classList),\n    dataset: Object.assign({}, el.dataset)\n  }));\n}\n","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"11E78BA8826CAD01050CB439142D894E"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":17870,"output":281,"cacheRead":47488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65639,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774147677530}}
