{"type":"message","id":"0d449890","parentId":"b0735543","timestamp":"2026-03-22T02:49:35.826Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在我成功获取了内容。从URL可以看到，页面已经跳转到了具体文档页面，category参数已经变成了`720698499150635520`。\n\n但是获取到的内容似乎是整个导航树的内容，而不是文档的正文内容。我需要找到真正的内容区域。\n\n让我重新提取内容，这次我需要排除导航菜单，只获取文档正文部分。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_81337f2449944e8b9a37a26d","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"\n() => {\n  // 获取当前页面的URL\n  const currentUrl = window.location.href;\n  \n  // 尝试找到右侧内容区域的容器（排除左侧导航）\n  // 通常内容区域会在一个单独的div中，并且有较大的文本内容\n  const possibleContentAreas = document.querySelectorAll('div[class*=\"content\"], div[class*=\"detail\"], div[class*=\"article\"], div[class*=\"main\"]');\n  \n  let contentArea = null;\n  let maxTextLength = 0;\n  \n  for (const area of possibleContentAreas) {\n    // 排除包含导航链接的区域\n    const links = area.querySelectorAll('a, div[cursor=pointer]');\n    const text = area.innerText;\n    \n    // 如果这个区域的链接数相对较少，但文本内容较多，可能是正文区域\n    if (links.length < 50 && text.length > maxTextLength) {\n      maxTextLength = text.length;\n      contentArea = area;\n    }\n  }\n  \n  if (contentArea) {\n    // 尝试获取标题\n    const titleElement = contentArea.querySelector('h1, h2, .title, .article-title');\n    const title = titleElement ? titleElement.textContent.trim() : '未知标题';\n    \n    return {\n      url: currentUrl,\n      title: title,\n      content: contentArea.innerText.substring(0, 10000),\n      contentLength: contentArea.innerText.length\n    };\n  }\n  \n  return {\n    url: currentUrl,\n    error: '未找到内容区域'\n  };\n}\n","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"ADBAF45F03907D36424ABD4D7C453243"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2854,"output":452,"cacheRead":67648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70954,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774147761386}}
