{"type":"message","id":"30d7ee9f","parentId":"92ebaa7c","timestamp":"2026-03-22T02:52:01.682Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"等待完成。现在让我尝试提取右侧内容区域的内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9a638ac9066d43ffa2708c96","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"\n() => {\n  // 获取当前URL\n  const currentUrl = window.location.href;\n  \n  // 尝试多种方式提取内容\n  const methods = [];\n  \n  // 方法1: 查找class包含content的div\n  const contentDivs = document.querySelectorAll('div[class*=\"content\"]');\n  for (const div of contentDivs) {\n    const text = div.innerText.trim();\n    if (text.length > 100) {\n      methods.push({\n        method: 'class-content',\n        length: text.length,\n        preview: text.substring(0, 200)\n      });\n    }\n  }\n  \n  // 方法2: 查找article标签\n  const articles = document.querySelectorAll('article');\n  for (const article of articles) {\n    const text = article.innerText.trim();\n    if (text.length > 100) {\n      methods.push({\n        method: 'article-tag',\n        length: text.length,\n        preview: text.substring(0, 200)\n      });\n    }\n  }\n  \n  // 方法3: 查找main标签\n  const mains = document.querySelectorAll('main');\n  for (const main of mains) {\n    const text = main.innerText.trim();\n    if (text.length > 100) {\n      methods.push({\n        method: 'main-tag',\n        length: text.length,\n        preview: text.substring(0, 200)\n      });\n    }\n  }\n  \n  // 方法4: 查找iframe\n  const iframes = document.querySelectorAll('iframe');\n  if (iframes.length > 0) {\n    methods.push({\n      method: 'iframe',\n      count: iframes.length,\n      src: Array.from(iframes).map(f => f.src)\n    });\n  }\n  \n  return {\n    url: currentUrl,\n    methods: methods\n  };\n}\n","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"ADBAF45F03907D36424ABD4D7C453243"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":155,"output":440,"cacheRead":75328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75923,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774147906769}}
{"type":"message","id":"c71e7658","parentId":"30d7ee9f","timestamp":"2026-03-22T02:52:01.839Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9a638ac9066d43ffa2708c96","toolName":"browser","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"ok\": true,\n  \"targetId\": \"ADBAF45F03907D36424ABD4D7C453243\",\n  \"url\": \"https://vip.kingdee.com/knowledge/specialDetail/218022218066869248?productLineId=29&lang=zh-CN\",\n  \"result\": {\n    \"url\": \"https://vip.kingdee.com/knowledge/specialDetail/218022218066869248?productLineId=29&lang=zh-CN\",\n    \"methods\": [\n      {\n        \"method\": \"class-content\",\n        \"length\": 145,\n        \"preview\": \"尊敬的用户，您当前使用的浏览器版本较低，这可能会导致您无法正常使用网站的某些功能。为了获得最佳浏览体验，我们建议您升级到最新版的浏览器。若当前浏览器已是最新版本，社区功能仍然无法使用，建议您更换Chrome、Firefox、Microsoft Edge、Safari最新版，获得更好的体验。\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"method\": \"class-content\",\n        \"length\": 8753,\n        \"preview\": \"开发平台\\n\\n动态与公告 NEW\\n重要通知 NEW\\n苍穹V8.0第三方包升级说明\\n苍穹V8.0及以上版本支持的JDK版本调整 NEW\\n苍穹V7.0.9第三方依赖包升级说明\\n整体介绍\\n概述\\n产品介绍\\n应用场景\\n苍穹开发平台整体介绍\\n开发环境搭建用户手册\\n开发服务器简介\\n开发者工具下载与安装\\n开发者工具离线登录与安装\\n环境安装与管理\\n（windows)数据库安装\\n（mac）数据库安装\\n环境安装\\n环境管理\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"method\": \"class-content\",\n        \"length\": 861,\n        \"preview\": \"安全防护\\n          安全防护\\n            开发服务云\\n          开发平台开发平台（专业版）模型资产管理定制开发平台无代码开发平台单据转换开发（BOTP）前端服务性能测试与分析余额模型AI基础服务\\n            系统服务云\\n          调度中心日志管理智能搜索第三方服务设置分布式管理\\n            基础服务云\\n          许可管理组\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"method\": \"class-content\",\n        \"length\": 285,\n        \"preview\": \"1\\n初识开发平台\\n概述\\n3\\n案例实战（开发案例说明）\\n简介：采购订货系统介绍\\n采购订货案例介绍\\n业务流程\\n采购申请单需求\\n采购订单需求\\n开发流程\\n5\\n案例实战（页面建模）\\n新建采购申请单&采购订单\\n设计采购申请单列表&采购订单列表\\n7\\n案例实战（插件开发）\\n基类选择\\n插件开发\\n插件注册\\n9\\n案例实战（发布应用）\\n应用发布\\n2\\n快速入门\\n创建第一个低代码应用\\n4\\n案例实战（云&应用开发）\\n云&应用开\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"method\": \"main-tag\",\n        \"length\": 8753,\n        \"preview\": \"开发平台\\n\\n动态与公告 NEW\\n重要通知 NEW\\n苍穹V8.0第三方包升级说明\\n苍穹V8.0及以上版本支持的JDK版本调整 NEW\\n苍穹V7.0.9第三方依赖包升级说明\\n整体介绍\\n概述\\n产品介绍\\n应用场景\\n苍穹开发平台整体介绍\\n开发环境搭建用户手册\\n开发服务器简介\\n开发者工具下载与安装\\n开发者工具离线登录与安装\\n环境安装与管理\\n（windows)数据库安装\\n（mac）数据库安装\\n环境安装\\n环境管理\"\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"ok":true,"targetId":"ADBAF45F03907D36424ABD4D7C453243","url":"https://vip.kingdee.com/knowledge/specialDetail/218022218066869248?productLineId=29&lang=zh-CN","result":{"url":"https://vip.kingdee.com/knowledge/specialDetail/218022218066869248?productLineId=29&lang=zh-CN","methods":[{"method":"class-content","length":145,"preview":"尊敬的用户，您当前使用的浏览器版本较低，这可能会导致您无法正常使用网站的某些功能。为了获得最佳浏览体验，我们建议您升级到最新版的浏览器。若当前浏览器已是最新版本，社区功能仍然无法使用，建议您更换Chrome、Firefox、Microsoft Edge、Safari最新版，获得更好的体验。"},{"method":"class-content","length":8753,"preview":"开发平台\n\n动态与公告 NEW\n重要通知 NEW\n苍穹V8.0第三方包升级说明\n苍穹V8.0及以上版本支持的JDK版本调整 NEW\n苍穹V7.0.9第三方依赖包升级说明\n整体介绍\n概述\n产品介绍\n应用场景\n苍穹开发平台整体介绍\n开发环境搭建用户手册\n开发服务器简介\n开发者工具下载与安装\n开发者工具离线登录与安装\n环境安装与管理\n（windows)数据库安装\n（mac）数据库安装\n环境安装\n环境管理"},{"method":"class-content","length":861,"preview":"安全防护\n          安全防护\n            开发服务云\n          开发平台开发平台（专业版）模型资产管理定制开发平台无代码开发平台单据转换开发（BOTP）前端服务性能测试与分析余额模型AI基础服务\n            系统服务云\n          调度中心日志管理智能搜索第三方服务设置分布式管理\n            基础服务云\n          许可管理组"},{"method":"class-content","length":285,"preview":"1\n初识开发平台\n概述\n3\n案例实战（开发案例说明）\n简介：采购订货系统介绍\n采购订货案例介绍\n业务流程\n采购申请单需求\n采购订单需求\n开发流程\n5\n案例实战（页面建模）\n新建采购申请单&采购订单\n设计采购申请单列表&采购订单列表\n7\n案例实战（插件开发）\n基类选择\n插件开发\n插件注册\n9\n案例实战（发布应用）\n应用发布\n2\n快速入门\n创建第一个低代码应用\n4\n案例实战（云&应用开发）\n云&应用开"},{"method":"main-tag","length":8753,"preview":"开发平台\n\n动态与公告 NEW\n重要通知 NEW\n苍穹V8.0第三方包升级说明\n苍穹V8.0及以上版本支持的JDK版本调整 NEW\n苍穹V7.0.9第三方依赖包升级说明\n整体介绍\n概述\n产品介绍\n应用场景\n苍穹开发平台整体介绍\n开发环境搭建用户手册\n开发服务器简介\n开发者工具下载与安装\n开发者工具离线登录与安装\n环境安装与管理\n（windows)数据库安装\n（mac）数据库安装\n环境安装\n环境管理"}]}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774147921832}}
{"type":"message","id":"3fc55427","parentId":"c71e7658","timestamp":"2026-03-22T02:52:14.272Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来点击后页面没有真正加载文档内容，而是显示了浏览器版本低的提示。这可能是因为：\n1. 页面检测到了headless Chrome，认为是旧版本浏览器\n2. 需要设置User-Agent或其他浏览器参数\n\n让我尝试另一种方法：使用web_fetch工具直接访问文档URL，或者尝试通过API获取文档内容。\n\n首先，让我检查一下页面是否有iframe或者其他加载内容的方式。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_443f7a836c0e4e3fad18894e","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"\n() => {\n  // 查找iframe\n  const iframes = document.querySelectorAll('iframe');\n  \n  // 查找可能的文档内容区域\n  const possibleContainers = document.querySelectorAll('[class*=\"doc\"], [class*=\"article\"], [class*=\"detail\"], [class*=\"special\"]');\n  \n  // 检查是否有Vue或React应用\n  const hasVue = document.querySelector('[data-v-]') !== null;\n  const hasReact = document.querySelector('[data-reactroot]') !== null;\n  \n  return {\n    iframes: iframes.length,\n    iframeSrcs: Array.from(iframes).map(f => f.src),\n    containers: possibleContainers.length,\n    containerClasses: Array.from(possibleContainers).map(c => c.className),\n    hasVue: hasVue,\n    hasReact: hasReact,\n    // 检查是否有__NUXT__或类似的全局变量\n    hasNuxt: typeof window.__NUXT__ !== 'undefined',\n    hasInitialState: typeof window.__INITIAL_STATE__ !== 'undefined'\n  };\n}\n","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"ADBAF45F03907D36424ABD4D7C453243"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1257,"output":356,"cacheRead":75456,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77069,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774147921841}}
{"type":"message","id":"7a64a323","parentId":"3fc55427","timestamp":"2026-03-22T02:52:14.524Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_443f7a836c0e4e3fad18894e","toolName":"browser","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"ok\": true,\n  \"targetId\": \"ADBAF45F03907D36424ABD4D7C453243\",\n  \"url\": \"https://vip.kingdee.com/knowledge/specialDetail/218022218066869248?productLineId=29&lang=zh-CN\",\n  \"result\": {\n    \"iframes\": 0,\n    \"iframeSrcs\": [],\n    \"containers\": 10,\n    \"containerClasses\": [\n      \"body-default clear-margin-down knowledge-specialDetail-id\",\n      \"lay_out_header_div knowledge-specialDetail-id-header-hidden\",\n      \"app-header app-header-bg no-scrolled page-header-knowledge-specialDetail-id no-login has-lang-switch\",\n      \"icon article\",\n      \"icon-article\",\n      \"knowledge-special-detail\",\n      \"knowledge-special-search center\",\n      \"knowledge-special-home\",\n      \"special-tool\",\n      \"article-search-tip\"\n    ],\n    \"hasVue\": false,\n    \"hasReact\": false,\n    \"hasNuxt\": true,\n    \"hasInitialState\": false\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"ok":true,"targetId":"ADBAF45F03907D36424ABD4D7C453243","url":"https://vip.kingdee.com/knowledge/specialDetail/218022218066869248?productLineId=29&lang=zh-CN","result":{"iframes":0,"iframeSrcs":[],"containers":10,"containerClasses":["body-default clear-margin-down knowledge-specialDetail-id","lay_out_header_div knowledge-specialDetail-id-header-hidden","app-header app-header-bg no-scrolled page-header-knowledge-specialDetail-id no-login has-lang-switch","icon article","icon-article","knowledge-special-detail","knowledge-special-search center","knowledge-special-home","special-tool","article-search-tip"],"hasVue":false,"hasReact":false,"hasNuxt":true,"hasInitialState":false}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774147934519}}
{"type":"message","id":"adb0c4e7","parentId":"7a64a323","timestamp":"2026-03-22T02:52:26.762Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来页面使用了Nuxt.js框架，有__NUXT__全局变量。页面URL也变了，说明点击确实触发了导航。\n\n让我尝试：\n1. 直接通过URL访问文档页面\n2. 或者提取__NUXT__中的数据\n3. 或者使用不同的选择器来获取内容\n\n首先让我尝试提取__NUXT__数据。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_607adf818f474ba1bbeeb761","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"\n() => {\n  // 尝试获取NUXT数据\n  if (typeof window.__NUXT__ !== 'undefined') {\n    return {\n      hasNuxt: true,\n      nuxtKeys: Object.keys(window.__NUXT__),\n      nuxtData: JSON.stringify(window.__NUXT__).substring(0, 2000)\n    };\n  }\n  \n  // 查找可能包含文档数据的script标签\n  const scripts = document.querySelectorAll('script');\n  let nuxtScript = null;\n  \n  for (const script of scripts) {\n    if (script.textContent.includes('window.__NUXT__')) {\n      nuxtScript = script.textContent.substring(0, 1000);\n      break;\n    }\n  }\n  \n  return {\n    hasNuxt: false,\n    hasNuxtScript: nuxtScript !== null,\n    nuxtScript: nuxtScript\n  };\n}\n","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"ADBAF45F03907D36424ABD4D7C453243"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":632,"output":308,"cacheRead":76672,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77612,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774147934526}}
