{"type":"message","id":"b6a00704","parentId":"4aa0a3cc","timestamp":"2026-03-22T02:52:52.738Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！我找到了所有目标文档的URL和entityId。现在我可以：\n1. 直接访问这些URL来获取文档内容\n2. 使用web_fetch工具来抓取每个文档\n\n我有8个文档URL，其中包含7个目标文档（\"单据体\"有两个，一个在控件使用指南下，一个在开发案例库下，我应该选择控件使用指南下的）。\n\n让我开始抓取第一个文档\"文本字段\"。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"完美！我找到了所有目标文档的URL。现在开始逐个抓取文档内容。\n\n**第1个文档：文本字段**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_945330ae712e48c58aee4846","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://vip.kingdee.com/knowledge/atlas/215128684791905280/detail","extractMode":"markdown"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1380,"output":160,"cacheRead":78464,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80004,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774147965641}}
