{"type":"message","id":"a6888005","parentId":"fc48285c","timestamp":"2026-03-22T02:53:22.407Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，回到专题页面。现在让我尝试一个不同的方法：\n1. 点击文档导航项\n2. 等待页面更新\n3. 通过__NUXT__数据获取当前文档的内容\n\n让我先点击\"文本字段\"并观察__NUXT__数据的变化。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_243ddd27c2134bc8b401bafb","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"\n() => {\n  // 查找\"文本字段\"元素\n  const elements = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('div')).filter(el => \n    el.textContent.trim() === '文本字段' && \n    el.parentElement && \n    el.parentElement.className === 'second-category'\n  );\n  \n  if (elements.length > 0) {\n    const element = elements[0];\n    \n    // 触发点击\n    const event = new MouseEvent('click', {\n      view: window,\n      bubbles: true,\n      cancelable: true\n    });\n    \n    element.dispatchEvent(event);\n    \n    return {\n      clicked: true,\n      message: '已点击文本字段'\n    };\n  }\n  \n  return { clicked: false };\n}\n","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"ADBAF45F03907D36424ABD4D7C453243"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":237,"output":258,"cacheRead":80640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81135,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774147992062}}
