{"type":"message","id":"e1dd79e0","parentId":"48331846","timestamp":"2026-03-22T02:54:00.291Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来__NUXT__数据中没有当前文档的详细内容。URL也没有变化，说明点击没有触发页面导航。\n\n让我尝试另一种方法：通过API直接获取文档内容。从之前的__NUXT__数据看，我知道文档的entityId，我可以尝试构建API请求。\n\n或者，让我尝试检查页面上是否有实际的内容区域显示文档内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7e65dc33ea1f41d3b1e99e18","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"screenshot","targetId":"ADBAF45F03907D36424ABD4D7C453243","type":"png"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":461,"output":118,"cacheRead":81344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81923,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774148027810}}
{"type":"message","id":"e64b5be7","parentId":"e1dd79e0","timestamp":"2026-03-22T02:54:02.196Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7e65dc33ea1f41d3b1e99e18","toolName":"browser","content":[{"type":"text","text":"MEDIA:/root/.openclaw/media/browser/88a04a63-ef6b-4b67-8bf6-c5ee3e07113e.png"},{"type":"image","data":"","mimeType":"image/jpeg"}],"details":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/media/browser/88a04a63-ef6b-4b67-8bf6-c5ee3e07113e.png","ok":true,"targetId":"ADBAF45F03907D36424ABD4D7C453243","url":"https://vip.kingdee.com/knowledge/specialDetail/218022218066869248?productLineId=29&lang=zh-CN"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774148042191}}
{"type":"message","id":"6d3e8489","parentId":"e64b5be7","timestamp":"2026-03-22T02:54:09.240Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我查看截图来了解当前页面的状态。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3d8deedd52e84327886088bc","name":"image","arguments":{"image":"/root/.openclaw/media/browser/88a04a63-ef6b-4b67-8bf6-c5ee3e07113e.png","prompt":"请详细描述这个页面的内容，特别是：\n1. 左侧导航栏的展开状态，是否显示了下级菜单\n2. 右侧内容区域显示了什么内容\n3. 是否有\"文本字段\"相关的文档内容显示\n4. 页面的整体布局结构"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":54366,"output":117,"cacheRead":9536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64019,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774148042198}}
{"type":"message","id":"2361cd7c","parentId":"6d3e8489","timestamp":"2026-03-22T02:54:54.240Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3d8deedd52e84327886088bc","toolName":"image","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### 1. 左侧导航栏的展开状态  \n左侧导航栏处于**展开状态**，显示了下级菜单。从图中可见，导航栏包含多级结构（如“基础组件”下展开显示“数据录入”“输入框”等子项），子项前有展开标识（如箭头或层级缩进），且部分子项带有“NEW”标记（如“数据录入”“输入框”），说明下级菜单已展开呈现。  \n\n\n### 2. 右侧内容区域显示的内容  \n右侧内容区域展示**文档类内容**，以编号（1 - 9）为序的条目化结构呈现，每个条目包含标题和子项列表：  \n- 条目1：“基础组件” → 子项“输入”；  \n- 条目3：“数据录入组件使用说明” → 子项“基础输入框组件”“输入框”“数字输入框”等；  \n- 条目4：“输入框组件&文本域组件” → 子项“&输入框组件”“文本域组件”等；  \n- 其他条目（如5 - 9）也以类似结构展示组件/功能说明。  \n此外，右侧顶部还包含一张“开发平台”宣传图（紫色背景，含“开发平台”“开发服务云”字样）。  \n\n\n### 3. “文本字段”相关文档内容的显示情况  \n**存在“文本字段”相关文档**。右侧内容中，“输入框”“基础输入框组件”“输入框组件&文本域组件”等条目直接关联文本字段（输入框、文本域属于文本输入类组件），属于文本字段相关的文档内容。  \n\n\n### 4. 页面的整体布局结构  \n页面采用**左右分栏布局**：  \n- **左侧**：导航栏（展开状态，展示多级菜单）；  \n- **右侧**：内容展示区（文档条目+宣传图）；  \n- **顶部**：工具栏（含搜索框、添加按钮、登录/注册按钮）；  \n- **中间**：弹窗（灰色半透明遮罩，显示“提示”信息，询问“是否确认删除该条目？”，含确认/取消按钮，遮挡部分内容）。  \n\n整体结构清晰，左侧导航引导内容分类，右侧聚焦文档详情，顶部工具栏提供操作入口，弹窗用于交互确认。"}],"details":{"model":"zai/glm-4.6v","image":"/root/.openclaw/media/browser/88a04a63-ef6b-4b67-8bf6-c5ee3e07113e.png","attempts":[]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774148094230}}
{"type":"message","id":"c21d56e4","parentId":"2361cd7c","timestamp":"2026-03-22T02:55:05.365Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"从截图描述看，页面上有一个弹窗（\"是否确认删除该条目？\"），这个弹窗遮挡了内容。这可能是点击导航项时意外触发的。\n\n让我关闭这个弹窗，然后重新尝试。我需要：\n1. 关闭弹窗\n2. 重新加载页面\n3. 使用更精确的元素选择器来点击导航项\n\n让我先关闭弹窗。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3dbe83614ad24a21b9274f2e","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"\n() => {\n  // 查找并点击取消按钮\n  const cancelButtons = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('button, div[role=button]')).filter(el => \n    el.textContent.trim() === '取消' || el.textContent.trim() === '关闭'\n  );\n  \n  if (cancelButtons.length > 0) {\n    cancelButtons[0].click();\n    return { closed: true };\n  }\n  \n  // 如果没有找到按钮，尝试按ESC键\n  const event = new KeyboardEvent('keydown', {\n    key: 'Escape',\n    code: 'Escape',\n    keyCode: 27,\n    bubbles: true\n  });\n  document.dispatchEvent(event);\n  \n  return { closed: false, tried: 'ESC' };\n}\n","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"ADBAF45F03907D36424ABD4D7C453243"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":641,"output":289,"cacheRead":63872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64802,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774148094243}}
