{"type":"message","id":"a8592577","parentId":"8d0465c7","timestamp":"2026-03-22T02:55:31.913Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"URL有误，让我使用正确的ID。正确的ID是218022218066869248。让我重新导航。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"根据技能指导，我意识到对于动态渲染的页面，需要采用更合适的方法。让我重新组织思路：\n\n1. **系统环境准备**：浏览器已启动\n2. **抓取目标评估**：已明确7个目标文档\n3. **登录障碍预处理**：从页面看，不需要登录即可访问\n4. **文档信息提取策略**：已从__NUXT__数据中获取到文档元数据\n\n现在的问题是：点击导航项后页面没有正确加载文档内容。让我尝试一个更直接的方法 - 通过API获取文档内容。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2c38082122b1430bbebbcdee","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"\nasync () => {\n  // 尝试通过API获取文档内容\n  const docId = '215128684791905280'; // 文本字段的entityId\n  \n  try {\n    const response = await fetch(`https://vip.kingdee.com/knowledge/api/knowledge/detail/${docId}`, {\n      method: 'GET',\n      credentials: 'include',\n      headers: {\n        'Accept': 'application/json',\n        'Content-Type': 'application/json'\n      }\n    });\n    \n    const data = await response.json();\n    \n    return {\n      success: true,\n      status: response.status,\n      data: JSON.stringify(data).substring(0, 2000)\n    };\n  } catch (error) {\n    return {\n      success: false,\n      error: error.message\n    };\n  }\n}\n","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"ADBAF45F03907D36424ABD4D7C453243"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":175,"output":367,"cacheRead":64896,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65438,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774148115360}}
